    <h2 class="subheading">FAQ - Click on the Questions to See the Answer!</h2>
  <div id="FAQ">
    <p class="q">Is everything fresh?</p>
    <p class="a">- Yes, everything is made in house, every single day by our incredibly talented bakers</p>
    <p class="q">Can I reserve bread?</p>
    <p class="a">- Yes, you can. You can contact us via phone and we can reserve a batch of bread to be picked up on the same day.</p>
    <p class="q">Do you have delivery options?</p>
    <p class="a">- You can now as of December 2020 order our goods via Deliveroo.</p>
    <p class="q">What allergens do your goods contain?</p>
    <p class="a">- Each of our goods display the allergens that they contain.</p>
    <p class="q">What forms of payment do you accept?</p>
    <p class="a">- We accept cash and all forms of Visa and MasterCard</p>
    <p class="q">What is the largest quantity that one person can buy?</p>
    <p class="a">- You can buy a maximum of 5 loaves of bread at a time; to allow other people to avail of our goods. However, if you require a
    large amount of goods, you can call a day before to reserve your order so we know to make more for that day. You can pick up your batch anytime
    that day.</p>
    <p class="q">Can I inquire about catering instore?</p>
    <p class="a">- You may however we prefer email for large catering jobs</p>
    <p class="q">Are your goods vegan?</p>
    <p class="a">- All goods are specified if they are vegan-friendly or not.</p>
    <p class="q">Do you make hampers full of goods available for purchase?</p>
    <p class="a">- We do produce hampers for sale around Christmas time. You can call if you require a hamper throughout the year and we will be happy to oblige.</p>
    <p class="q">Do you have gluten free options?</p>
    <p class="a">- All goods are specified if they are vegan friendly or not.</p>
  </div>

